           ^--- unsorted starts here

--- Pass 1 (pos=0, find min in [64,34,25,12,22,11,90]) ---
  Scanning: min found at index 5 (value=11)
  Swap arr[0] and arr[5]: 64 ↔ 11
  Result: [11, 34, 25, 12, 22, 64, 90]
